    trusted by industry leading teams like Google, Figma, Revolut, and Shopify
  </p>
  <div class='w-full flex flex-col gap-y-6'>
    <div
      class='child:md:w-auto flex flex-wrap gap-y-6 h-[34px] md:h-[31px] lg:h-[46px] child:w-[96px] w-full justify-between'
    >
      <Image
        src={ImageGoogle}
        alt='google-logo'
        loading='lazy'
        decoding='async'
        class='h-full md:hidden md:appearance-none'
      />
